item.title: Why I Made This Website
item.description: I haven’t always wanted my own website. In fact, I was long convinced that creating my own website would be a waste of time and effort. Anyone can create a Linkedin profile in less than an hour. On the other hand, it might take tens of hours to get your personal website to a point that employers or customers might be impressed by. With that level of work, I thought I might as well avoid the whole process and contract out if I ever really needed a site.
